       <div class="container">
         <div class="row">
          <div class="col-10 offset-1">
            <p class="lead"><span class="numbers display-4 text-white pl-2">1: &nbsp;</span>Name the faces and factions that limit us in effectively end the cyclical degradation of the Earth.</p>
            <p class="lead"><span class="numbers display-4 text-white">2: &nbsp;</span>Clearly illustrate what repair will look like.</p>
            <p class="lead"><span class="numbers display-4 text-white">3: &nbsp;</span>Create a loosely organized network of critical humanists passionate about saving the Earth.</p>
