     <!-- DESCRIPTION -->
      <section id="description" class="pb-5">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3 class="display-4 text-center">Organizing</h3>
              <hr>
              <p class="lead text-right">
                In 6 groups of 10 master's students we will combine our previous research of our group's sub-topic and see what
                humanistic insights are waiting to be contributed to the common understanding of the environment, whether it
                be climactic, urban or rural.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3 class="display-4 text-center">Creating</h3>
              <hr>
              <p class="lead">
                Each subgroup will be responsible to create it's own document over the first day and a half. The second half of the
                second day will be dedicated to group critique and assembling the documents into a mosaic meta-document on the state
                of the environment from our perspectives.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

